Package com.charliai.activities.api

Class Workflow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.charliai.activities.api.Workflow
  • public class Workflow
extends java.lang.Object
    The Workflow class provides access to workflow details within activity requests; including plans and steps. This class is intended to be a representation of the workflow message details.
    Author:
    kevincollins
